{"tid":1703770,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有關自稱入境處人員公開發表言論一事","createTime":"2019-11-10T12:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:39.000Z","uid":8833,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d573e28dbf646215dde5bbec5a7dcc8d479f0974","tid":1703770,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/10/P2019111000623.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F10%2FP2019111000623.htm&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=848ccab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/10/P2019111000623.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有關自稱入境處人員公開發表言論一事<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　就近日有自稱入境事務處（入境處）人員公開發表對政府及時下局勢的言論，入境處今日（十一月十日）表示目前並沒有證據顯示該等言論確由入境處人員所發出。<br />\n<br />\n　　處方並再次重申一直堅定支持特區政府依法施政、支持警方嚴正執法，以求盡早止暴制亂，恢復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n　　處方提醒任何人士如冒認公職人員，可能已觸犯法律，一經定罪，最高刑罰可被判入獄。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於入境處屬下人員，處方一直有既定溝通渠道，讓屬下人員可適當發表意見，惟必須嚴格按照公務員相關守則及部門相關指引及程序。<br />\n<br />\n　　入境處一向極為重視人員紀律，若發現任何人員違反《公務員守則》或部門紀律，必定會嚴肅跟進和處理。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月10日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間18時26分<br />\n<br />\n做人做狗自己揀<br />\n不做政府走狗<br />\n夠齊心就一定得"},{"pid":"095f3a484edef8876e953a4ee1121e22959a812e","tid":1703770,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">齊心萬事得</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9aa251c3601a71052c5e8a27ec78db759e27215","tid":1703770,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4863dfcd4bf5ecbba967694eb9e4a28e310693","tid":1703770,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T1